    "headline": "S&P Global Declares Second Quarter Dividend",
    "summary": "The Board of Directors of S&P Global (NYSE: SPGI) has approved a cash dividend on the Company's common stock for the second quarter of 2026. The dividend of $0.97 is payable on June 10, 2026, to shareholders of record on May 29, 2026. The annualized dividend rate is $3.88 per share.",
